title: Someone On The Show Heard A Rumor About Bobby + One Second Song Game + Amy Wants To Know Why Bobby Called DWTS
itunes:title: Someone On The Show Heard A Rumor About Bobby + One Second Song Game + Amy Wants To Know Why Bobby Called DWTS
description:
Someone on the show heard a rumor. Bobby lets them tell the rumor and answers whether it’s true or not. We all play the One Second of Song game where we have to guess the song just by hearing 1 second of the beginning of it. Also, Amy saw a headline online about Bobby that said he recently called Dancing With The Stars about something she hadn’t heard about.
